借到季尾咋，extend多一年係option<br />
<br />
A statement on <a href="http://Juventus.com" data-sr-url="https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FJuventus.com&d=fEJCtfATBeMWJ6YDVJZPMvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=e8361868" data-auto-link target="_blank">Juventus.com</a> read: &ldquo;The agreement also grants to Chelsea the options to extend the duration of the loan until 30 June 2020, for a consideration of 18m euros (&pound;15.7m) to be paid in 2019-20 financial year, or to acquire the registration rights of the player on a permanent basis for 36m euros (31.3m) to be paid in two financial years.&rdquo;

